k\"><use xlink:href=\"#ico-feedback\"></use></svg><span class=\"zDocsFeedbackButtonText\"> Feedback</span></span></div></div><div class=\"zDocsTopicActionsMobile\"><button aria-label=\"Show topic actions\" data-toggle=\"dropdown\" id=\"zDocsTopicActionsMobile\"><svg aria-hidden=\"true\" class=\"ico-ellipsis-h\"><use xlink:href=\"#ico-ellipsis-h\"></use></svg></button><div class=\"dropdown-menu zDocsDropdownMenu zDocsTopicActionsMobileDropdown dropdown-menu-right\"></div></div><div style=\"flex-basis: 100%; height: 0px;\"></div><ul class=\"zDocsTopicPageDetails\"><li class=\"zDocsTopicPageDate css-cinqea\">Last Updated<span class=\"css-cinqea\">Okt 09, 2024</span></li><li class=\"zDocsAiTopicSummaryDetailsItem\"><button class=\"zDocsAiTopicSummaryButton\"><svg aria-hidden=\"true\" class=\"ico-topic-summary\"><use xlink:href=\"#ico-topic-summary\"></use></svg>Summarize</button></li><li class=\"spacer\" role=\"presentation\"></li><div class=\"zDocsLabelWrapper\"><ul><li class=\"zDocsLabel\"><a aria-describedby=\"hyperLinkFacetsTooltip\" class=\"css-ettsdk\" data-tooltip-content=\"Search all site by tag: Uniface\" data-tooltip-id=\"hyperLinkFacetsTooltip\" href=\"/de-DE/search?labelkey=prod_uniface\" stylesprops=\"[object Object]\"><svg aria-label=\"Tag\" class=\"ico-tag\" role=\"img\"><use xlink:href=\"#ico-tag\"></use></svg>Uniface</a></li><li class=\"zDocsLabel\"><a aria-describedby=\"hyperLinkFacetsTooltip\" class=\"css-ettsdk\" data-tooltip-content=\"Search all site by tag: 10.4\" data-tooltip-id=\"hyperLinkFacetsTooltip\" href=\"/de-DE/search?labelkey=uniface_10.4\" stylesprops=\"[object Object]\"><svg aria-label=\"Tag\" class=\"ico-tag\" role=\"img\"><use xlink:href=\"#ico-tag\"></use></svg>10.4</a></li></ul></div></ul></header><div class=\"zDocsTopicPageBody\" data-prismjs-copy=\"Copy\" data-prismjs-copy-error=\"Copy failed! Use Ctrl + C instead.\" data-prismjs-copy-success=\"Copied!\"><div class=\"zDocsTopicPageBodyContent wide\" dir=\"ltr\"><div id=\"zDocsAiSummaryContaineruniface_104euw1665702582150.html\"></div><div><article class=\"hascomments\" data-page=\"bundle:uniface_104/enus/euw1665702582150.html\" id=\"bundle:uniface_104/enus/euw1665702582150.html\"><main role=\"main\"><article aria-labelledby=\"ariaid-title1\" class=\"dita\" id=\"euw1665702582150\" role=\"article\">\n<h1 class=\"title topictitle1\" id=\"ariaid-title1\">\n                          \n Form\n   </h1>\n<div class=\"body refbody\"><p class=\"shortdesc\">A Form is a stateful presentation Component that enables users to view and modify data in a Windows or character mode application.\n </p>\n<section class=\"section\" id=\"euw1665702582150__section_txp_14n_mwb\"><h2 class=\"title sectiontitle\" id=\"d497811e51\">Characteristics</h2>\n<div class=\"table-wrap\"><table class=\"table\" count-columns=\"2\" id=\"euw1665702582150__table_d10589e1_d10590e1_d10591e1\"><caption></caption><colgroup><col/><col/></colgroup><thead class=\"thead\">\n<tr class=\"row\" dir=\"ltr\">\n<th class=\"entry\" dir=\"ltr\" id=\"euw1665702582150__table_d10589e1_d10590e1_d10591e1__entry__1\">\n<p class=\"p\">Characteristics</p>\n</th>\n<th class=\"entry\" dir=\"ltr\" id=\"euw1665702582150__table_d10589e1_d10590e1_d10591e1__entry__2\"></th>\n</tr>\n</thead><tbody class=\"tbody\">\n<tr class=\"row\" dir=\"ltr\">\n<td class=\"entry\" dir=\"ltr\" headers=\"euw1665702582150__table_d10589e1_d10590e1_d10591e1__entry__1\">\n<p class=\"p\">Icon:</p>\n</td>\n<td class=\"entry\" dir=\"ltr\" headers=\"euw1665702582150__table_d10589e1_d10590e1_d10591e1__entry__2\">\n<p class=\"p\"><img alt=\"Icon\" class=\"image\" id=\"euw1665702582150__image_bcn_d4n_mwb\" src=\"https://docs-be.rocketsoftware.com/bundle/uniface_104/page/component.png?_LANG=enus\"/></p>\n</td>\n</tr>\n<tr class=\"row\" dir=\"ltr\">\n<td class=\"entry\" dir=\"ltr\" headers=\"euw1665702582150__table_d10589e1_d10590e1_d10591e1__entry__1\">\n<p class=\"p\">Object type code:</p>\n</td>\n<td class=\"entry\" dir=\"ltr\" headers=\"euw1665702582150__table_d10589e1_d10590e1_d10591e1__entry__2\">\n<p class=\"p\">\n<span class=\"keyword cmdname\">cpt</span>\n</p>\n</td>\n</tr>\n<tr class=\"row\" dir=\"ltr\">\n<td class=\"entry\" dir=\"ltr\" headers=\"euw1665702582150__table_d10589e1_d10590e1_d10591e1__entry__1\">\n<p class=\"p\">Main Development Object?</p>\n</td>\n<td class=\"entry\" dir=\"ltr\" headers=\"euw1665702582150__table_d10589e1_d10590e1_d10591e1__entry__2\">\n<p class=\"p\">Yes</p>\n</td>\n</tr>\n<tr class=\"row\" dir=\"ltr\">\n<td class=\"entry\" dir=\"ltr\" headers=\"euw1665702582150__table_d10589e1_d10590e1_d10591e1__entry__1\">\n<p class=\"p\">Has layout?</p>\n</td>\n<td class=\"entry\" dir=\"ltr\" headers=\"euw1665702582150__table_d10589e1_d10590e1_d10591e1__entry__2\">\n<p class=\"p\">Yes</p>\n</td>\n</tr>\n<tr class=\"row\" dir=\"ltr\">\n<td class=\"entry\" dir=\"ltr\" headers=\"euw1665702582150__table_d10589e1_d10590e1_d10591e1__entry__1\">\n<p class=\"p\">Layout binding?</p>\n</td>\n<td class=\"entry\" dir=\"ltr\" headers=\"euw1665702582150__table_d10589e1_d10590e1_d10591e1__entry__2\">\n<p class=\"p\">Implicit</p>\n</td>\n</tr>\n<tr class=\"row\" dir=\"ltr\">\n<td class=\"entry\" dir=\"ltr\" headers=\"euw1665702582150__table_d10589e1_d10590e1_d10591e1__entry__1\">\n<p class=\"p\">Part of:</p>\n</td>\n<td class=\"entry\" dir=\"ltr\" headers=\"euw1665702582150__table_d10589e1_d10590e1_d10591e1__entry__2\">\n<p class=\"p\">—</p>\n</td>\n</tr>\n<tr class=\"row\" dir=\"ltr\">\n<td class=\"entry\" dir=\"ltr\" headers=\"euw1665702582150__table_d10589e1_d10590e1_d10591e1__entry__1\">\n<p class=\"p\">Contains:</p>\n</td>\n<td class=\"entry\" dir=\"ltr\" headers=\"euw1665702582150__table_d10589e1_d10590e1_d10591e1__entry__2\">\n<p class=\"p\">\n<a class=\"xref\" data-bundleid=\"uniface_104\" data-navpath=\"yth1665702550544.html\" href=\"/de-DE/bundle/uniface_104/page/yth1665702550544.html\" title=\"A Component Entity is a Development Object that represents data that is owned by a Component. It is part of the Component’s structure and is maintained as part of the Component, although it may reference and inherit from a Modeled Entity.\">Component Entity</a>, <a class=\"xref\" data-bundleid=\"uniface_104\" data-navpath=\"wyt1665702609153.html\" href=\"/de-DE/bundle/uniface_104/page/wyt1665702609153.html\" title=\"A Label is a Development Object that contains text that appears on a presentation component. Labels have properties, but most cannot be set dynamically.\">Label</a>, <a class=\"xref\" data-bundleid=\"uniface_104\" data-navpath=\"jgi1665702550212.html\" href=\"/de-DE/bundle/uniface_104/page/jgi1665702550212.html\" title=\"A Property is a named, typed attribute of Development Object that defines a characteristic or behavior of the object. Each property has a descriptive name, a literal name, a data type, and a value. If no value is specified, a default value may be used.\">Property</a>, <a class=\"xref\" data-bundleid=\"uniface_104\" data-navpath=\"cny1665702550298.html\" href=\"/de-DE/bundle/uniface_104/page/cny1665702550298.html\" title=\"A Code Container is a type of Property that holds code, such as ProcScript, JavaScript, or HTML. It can contain one or more code modules, such as triggers, operations, functions, or entries, or HTML for the layout.\">Code Container</a>\n</p>\n</td>\n</tr>\n<tr class=\"row\" dir=\"ltr\">\n<td class=\"entry\" dir=\"ltr\" headers=\"euw1665702582150__table_d10589e1_d10590e1_d10591e1__entry__1\">\n<p class=\"p\">Generalization:</p>\n</td>\n<td class=\"entry\" dir=\"ltr\" headers=\"euw1665702582150__table_d10589e1_d10590e1_d10591e1__entry__2\">\n<p class=\"p\">\n<a class=\"xref\" data-bundleid=\"uniface_104\" data-navpath=\"ifc1665702608950.html\" href=\"/de-DE/bundle/uniface_104/page/ifc1665702608950.html\" title=\"A Component is a Main Development Object that defines an executable part of an application. It defines the data structure used to access data, the layout (if applicable) used to present it, and the actions used to modify, validate, and store data.\">Component</a>\n</p>\n</td>\n</tr>\n<tr class=\"row\" dir=\"ltr\">\n<td class=\"entry\" dir=\"ltr\" headers=\"euw1665702582150__table_d10589e1_d10590e1_d10591e1__entry__1\">\n<p class=\"p\">Specializations:</p>\n</td>\n<td class=\"entry\" dir=\"ltr\" headers=\"euw1665702582150__table_d10589e1_d10590e1_d10591e1__entry__2\">\n<p class=\"p\">—</p>\n</td>\n</tr>\n<tr class=\"row\" dir=\"ltr\">\n<td class=\"entry\" dir=\"ltr\" headers=\"euw1665702582150__table_d10589e1_d10590e1_d10591e1__entry__1\">\n<p class=\"p\">Compilation Output:</p>\n</td>\n<td class=\"entry\" dir=\"ltr\" headers=\"euw1665702582150__table_d10589e1_d10590e1_d10591e1__entry__2\">\n<p class=\"p\">\n<a class=\"xref\" data-bundleid=\"uniface_104\" data-navpath=\"ird1665702714456.html\" href=\"/de-DE/bundle/uniface_104/page/ird1665702714456.html\" title=\"A Signature is a Development Object that describes the remote interface of a component, or modeled entity operation. Signatures for Uniface components and modeled entity operations are automatically generated, but signatures for non-Uniface components that Uniface can call at runtime, must be explicitly defined.\">Signature</a>, <span class=\"ph filepath\">\n<var class=\"keyword varname\">FormName</var>.frm</span>, <span class=\"ph filepath\">\n<var class=\"keyword varname\">FormName</var>.sig</span>\n</p>\n</td>\n</tr>\n<tr class=\"row\" dir=\"ltr\">\n<td class=\"entry\" dir=\"ltr\" headers=\"euw1665702582150__table_d10589e1_d10590e1_d10591e1__entry__1\">\n<p class=\"p\">URI format:</p>\n</td>\n<td class=\"entry\" dir=\"ltr\" headers=\"euw1665702582150__table_d10589e1_d10590e1_d10591e1__entry__2\">\n<p class=\"p\">\n<code class=\"ph codeph\">cpt:<var class=\"keyword varname\">FormName</var>\n</code>\n</p>\n</td>\n</tr>\n</tbody></table></div>\n</section>\n<section class=\"section\" id=\"euw1665702582150__section_khr_f4n_mwb\"><h2 class=\"title sectiontitle\" id=\"d497811e326\">Specialization</h2>\n<p class=\"p\" id=\"euw1665702582150__p_d95504e1_d95505e1_d95506e1\">Form specializes Component in the following ways:</p>\n<ul class=\"ul\" id=\"euw1665702582150__ul_b3x_g4n_mwb\">\n<li class=\"li\" id=\"euw1665702582150__li_d38063e1_d38064e1_d38065e1\">\n<p class=\"p\" id=\"euw1665702582150__p_d95507e1_d95508e1_d95509e1\">It has a layout that is part of the component\n            itself.</p>\n</li>\n<li class=\"li\" id=\"euw1665702582150__li_d38066e1_d38067e1_d38068e1\">\n<p class=\"p\" id=\"euw1665702582150__p_d95510e1_d95511e1_d95512e1\">It has specialized triggers.</p>\n</li>\n<li class=\"li\" id=\"euw1665702582150__li_d38069e1_d38070e1_d38071e1\">\n<p class=\"p\" id=\"euw1665702582150__p_d95513e1_d95514e1_d95515e1\">It compiles to a deployable runtime component\n              (<span class=\"ph filepath\">.frm</span>) and signature.</p>\n</li>\n</ul>\n</section>\n<section class=\"section\" id=\"euw1665702582150__section_c3j_h4n_mwb\"><h2 class=\"title sectiontitle\" id=\"d497811e359\">Properties</h2>\n<p class=\"p\" id=\"euw1665702582150__p_d95519e1_d95520e1_d95521e1\">Object Properties:</p>\n<ul class=\"ul\" id=\"euw1665702582150__ul_h2t_34n_mwb\">\n<li class=\"li\" id=\"euw1665702582150__li_d38072e1_d38073e1_d38074e1\">\n<a class=\"xref\" data-bundleid=\"uniface_104\" data-navpath=\"jrq1665702585385.html\" href=\"/de-DE/bundle/uniface_104/page/jrq1665702585385.html\" title=\"Name of the development object, which uniquely identifies it.\">Name</a>\n</li>\n<li class=\"li\" id=\"euw1665702582150__li_d38075e1_d38076e1_d38077e1\">\n<a class=\"xref\" data-bundleid=\"uniface_104\" data-navpath=\"owq1665702585461.html\" href=\"/de-DE/bundle/uniface_104/page/owq1665702585461.html\" title=\"Type of Development Object. Read only.\">Type</a>\n</li>\n<li class=\"li\" id=\"euw1665702582150__li_d38078e1_d38079e1_d38080e1\">\n<a class=\"xref\" data-bundleid=\"uniface_104\" data-navpath=\"ybn1665702585544.html\" href=\"/de-DE/bundle/uniface_104/page/ybn1665702585544.html\" title=\"Complete URI of the Development Object. Read only.\">Location</a>\n</li>\n<li class=\"li\" id=\"euw1665702582150__li_d38081e1_d38082e1_d38083e1\">\n<a class=\"xref\" data-bundleid=\"uniface_104\" data-navpath=\"xrw1665702585620.html\" href=\"/de-DE/bundle/uniface_104/page/xrw1665702585620.html\" title=\"Use this property to briefly describe the development object in up to 256 Unicode characters.\">Description</a>\n</li>\n<li class=\"li\" id=\"euw1665702582150__li_d38084e1_d38085e1_d38086e1\">\n<a class=\"xref\" data-bundleid=\"uniface_104\" data-navpath=\"ipc1665702585697.html\" href=\"/de-DE/bundle/uniface_104/page/ipc1665702585697.html\" title=\"Use this property to provide comments or instructions for the selected development object. You can use the toolbar and standard Windows keyboard shortcuts to format the text, copy and paste, and undo and redo edits.\">Documentation</a>\n</li>\n</ul>\n<p class=\"p\" id=\"euw1665702582150__p_d95522e1_d95523e1_d95524e1\">Source Properties:</p>\n<ul class=\"ul\" id=\"euw1665702582150__ul_r2t_34n_mwb\">\n<li class=\"li\" id=\"euw1665702582150__li_d38087e1_d38088e1_d38089e1\">\n<a class=\"xref\" data-bundleid=\"uniface_104\" data-navpath=\"cnn1665702762358.html\" href=\"/de-DE/bundle/uniface_104/page/cnn1665702762358.html\" title=\"Read-only property the records the date and time when the object was last modified. The value is set by Uniface.\">Date Modified</a>\n</li>\n</ul>\n<p class=\"p\" id=\"euw1665702582150__p_d95525e1_d95526e1_d95527e1\">Configuration Properties:</p>\n<ul class=\"ul\" id=\"euw1665702582150__ul_t2t_34n_mwb\">\n<li class=\"li\" id=\"euw1665702582150__li_d38090e1_d38091e1_d38092e1\">\n<a class=\"xref\" data-bundleid=\"uniface_104\" data-navpath=\"wyl1665702688770.html\" href=\"/de-DE/bundle/uniface_104/page/wyl1665702688770.html\" title=\"Specifies the library containing the global objects used by the component or application shell. If no library is specified, the library defined for the application shell is used. Otherwise, SYSTEM_LIBRARY is used as the default.\">Library</a>\n</li>\n<li class=\"li\" id=\"euw1665702582150__li_d38093e1_d38094e1_d38095e1\">\n<a class=\"xref\" data-bundleid=\"uniface_104\" data-navpath=\"dfn1665702688838.html\" href=\"/de-DE/bundle/uniface_104/page/dfn1665702688838.html\" title=\"This property determines whether the component is a modeled component.\">Is Modeled Component</a>\n</li>\n<li class=\"li\" id=\"euw1665702582150__li_d38096e1_d38097e1_d38098e1\">\n<a class=\"xref\" data-bundleid=\"uniface_104\" data-navpath=\"mwa1665702688914.html\" href=\"/de-DE/bundle/uniface_104/page/mwa1665702688914.html\" title=\"This property specifies the name of the modeled component from which this component is derived.\">Modeled Component</a>\n</li>\n</ul>\n<p class=\"p\" id=\"euw1665702582150__p_d95528e1_d95529e1_d95530e1\">Behavior Properties:</p>\n<ul class=\"ul\" id=\"euw1665702582150__ul_aft_34n_mwb\">\n<li class=\"li\" id=\"euw1665702582150__li_d38099e1_d38100e1_d38101e1\">\n<a class=\"xref\" data-bundleid=\"uniface_104\" data-navpath=\"obc1665703043525.html\" href=\"/de-DE/bundle/uniface_104/page/obc1665703043525.html\" title=\"Specifies the type of Uniface Component.\">Component Type</a></li>\n<li class=\"li\" id=\"euw1665702582150__li_d38102e1_d38103e1_d38104e1\">\n<a class=\"xref\" data-bundleid=\"uniface_104\" data-navpath=\"qsg1665702688984.html\" href=\"/de-DE/bundle/uniface_104/page/qsg1665702688984.html\" title=\"Determines the degree to which data in the component can be edited and stored.\">Data Access</a>\n</li>\n<li class=\"li\" id=\"euw1665702582150__li_d38105e1_d38106e1_d38107e1\">\n<a class=\"xref\" data-bundleid=\"uniface_104\" data-navpath=\"ypq1665702689055.html\" href=\"/de-DE/bundle/uniface_104/page/ypq1665702689055.html\" title=\"Specifies whether the component definition is cached in memory.\">Component Behavior</a>\n</li>\n<li class=\"li\" id=\"euw1665702582150__li_d38108e1_d38109e1_d38110e1\">\n<a class=\"xref\" data-bundleid=\"uniface_104\" data-navpath=\"mxz1665703028639.html\" href=\"/de-DE/bundle/uniface_104/page/mxz1665703028639.html\" title=\"Controls whether the component instance runs in attached mode, meaning that it is created by another component and is deleted when the parent component instance is deleted.\">Attachment</a>\n</li>\n</ul>\n<p class=\"p\" id=\"euw1665702582150__p_d95531e1_d95532e1_d95533e1\">Database I/O Properties:</p>\n<ul class=\"ul\" id=\"euw1665702582150__ul_ift_34n_mwb\">\n<li class=\"li\" id=\"euw1665702582150__li_d38111e1_d38112e1_d38113e1\">\n<a class=\"xref\" data-bundleid=\"uniface_104\" data-navpath=\"iku1665702689266.html\" href=\"/de-DE/bundle/uniface_104/page/iku1665702689266.html\" title=\"Name of the Keyboard Translation Table used to interpret field data upon input.\">Input Translation</a>\n</li>\n<li class=\"li\" id=\"euw1665702582150__li_d38114e1_d38115e1_d38116e1\">\n<a class=\"xref\" data-bundleid=\"uniface_104\" data-navpath=\"dbe1665702689335.html\" href=\"/de-DE/bundle/uniface_104/page/dbe1665702689335.html\" title=\"Name of the Keyboard Translation Table used to convert field data upon output.\">Output Translation</a>\n</li>\n</ul>\n<p class=\"p\" id=\"euw1665702582150__p_d95534e1_d95535e1_d95536e1\">Presentation Properties:</p>\n<ul class=\"ul\" id=\"euw1665702582150__ul_mft_34n_mwb\">\n<li class=\"li\" id=\"euw1665702582150__li_d38117e1_d38118e1_d38119e1\">\n<a class=\"xref\" data-bundleid=\"uniface_104\" data-navpath=\"wfn1665703029011.html\" href=\"/de-DE/bundle/uniface_104/page/wfn1665703029011.html\" title=\"This property defines an associative list of properties that control the appearance and behavior of a form component running in a Windows environment.\">Window Properties</a>\n</li>\n<li class=\"li\" id=\"euw1665702582150__li_d38120e1_d38121e1_d38122e1\">\n<a class=\"xref\" data-bundleid=\"uniface_104\" data-navpath=\"myt1665702689407.html\" href=\"/de-DE/bundle/uniface_104/page/myt1665702689407.html\" title=\"Title displayed in the window title bar or browser tab when the application shell, form, or server page is run. If no title is specified, the object name is displayed.\">Title</a>\n</li>\n<li class=\"li\" id=\"euw1665702582150__li_d38123e1_d38124e1_d38125e1\">\n<a class=\"xref\" data-bundleid=\"uniface_104\" data-navpath=\"xtq1665702714794.html\" href=\"/de-DE/bundle/uniface_104/page/xtq1665702714794.html\" title=\"This property specifies the name of the panel that is displayed with the form or application shell at runtime.\">Panel</a>\n</li>\n<li class=\"li\" id=\"euw1665702582150__li_d38126e1_d38127e1_d38128e1\">\n<a class=\"xref\" data-bundleid=\"uniface_104\" data-navpath=\"txw1665702714934.html\" href=\"/de-DE/bundle/uniface_104/page/txw1665702714934.html\" title=\"Position of the panel for a form or application shell when displayed at runtime.\">Panel Position</a>\n</li>\n<li class=\"li\" id=\"euw1665702582150__li_d38129e1_d38130e1_d38131e1\">\n<a class=\"xref\" data-bundleid=\"uniface_104\" data-navpath=\"glg1665702714695.html\" href=\"/de-DE/bundle/uniface_104/page/glg1665702714695.html\" title=\"Name of the menu bar initially displayed for the current form or application shell.\">Menu Bar</a>\n</li>\n<li class=\"li\" id=\"euw1665702582150__li_d38132e1_d38133e1_d38134e1\">\n<a class=\"xref\" data-bundleid=\"uniface_104\" data-navpath=\"nnt1665702586853.html\" href=\"/de-DE/bundle/uniface_104/page/nnt1665702586853.html\" title=\"Name of the pop-up menu object to display when the user clicks the mouse button in this component, entity, or field.\">Pop-up Menu</a>\n</li>\n<li class=\"li\" id=\"euw1665702582150__li_d38135e1_d38136e1_d38137e1\">\n<a class=\"xref\" data-bundleid=\"uniface_104\" data-navpath=\"pcn1665702834745.html\" href=\"/de-DE/bundle/uniface_104/page/pcn1665702834745.html\" title=\"Form property that determines whether the form can be moved independently of other forms, or whether it overlays another form.\">Is Independent Form</a>\n</li>\n<li class=\"li\" id=\"euw1665702582150__li_d38138e1_d38139e1_d38140e1\">\n<a class=\"xref\" data-bundleid=\"uniface_104\" data-navpath=\"xvf1665702834817.html\" href=\"/de-DE/bundle/uniface_104/page/xvf1665702834817.html\" title=\"Form property that determines whether open forms are removed from the display when this form is run. True or False (Default).\">Hide Previous</a>\n</li>\n<li class=\"li\" id=\"euw1665702582150__li_d38141e1_d38142e1_d38143e1\">\n<a class=\"xref\" data-bundleid=\"uniface_104\" data-navpath=\"wwg1665702587409.html\" href=\"/de-DE/bundle/uniface_104/page/wwg1665702587409.html\" title=\"Code that identifies a Uniface index color, which represents a combination of background and foreground colors. Applicable only to Form components. Deprecated.\">Index Color</a>\n</li>\n<li class=\"li\" id=\"euw1665702582150__li_d38144e1_d38145e1_d38146e1\">\n<a class=\"xref\" data-bundleid=\"uniface_104\" data-navpath=\"kff1665703029082.html\" href=\"/de-DE/bundle/uniface_104/page/kff1665703029082.html\" title=\"Position of the top of the form in relation to the application window, in character cells.\">Top</a>\n</li>\n<li class=\"li\" id=\"euw1665702582150__li_d38147e1_d38148e1_d38149e1\">\n<a class=\"xref\" data-bundleid=\"uniface_104\" data-navpath=\"qnw1665703029152.html\" href=\"/de-DE/bundle/uniface_104/page/qnw1665703029152.html\" title=\"Position of the side of the form in relation to the application window, in character cells.\">Left</a>\n</li>\n<li class=\"li\" id=\"euw1665702582150__li_d38150e1_d38151e1_d38152e1\">\n<a class=\"xref\" data-bundleid=\"uniface_104\" data-navpath=\"nik1665703029224.html\" href=\"/de-DE/bundle/uniface_104/page/nik1665703029224.html\" title=\"Height of the form or report, in character cells. In the Layout Editor, this is represented by a blue dashed line.\">Height</a>\n</li>\n<li class=\"li\" id=\"euw1665702582150__li_d38153e1_d38154e1_d38155e1\">\n<a class=\"xref\" data-bundleid=\"uniface_104\" data-navpath=\"rtt1665703029293.html\" href=\"/de-DE/bundle/uniface_104/page/rtt1665703029293.html\" title=\"Width of the form or report, in character cells. In the Layout Editor, this is represented by a blue dashed line.\">Width</a>\n</li>\n</ul>\n<p class=\"p\" id=\"euw1665702582150__p_d95537e1_d95538e1_d95539e1\">Character Mode Properties:</p>\n<ul class=\"ul\" id=\"euw1665702582150__ul_lgt_34n_mwb\">\n<li class=\"li\" id=\"euw1665702582150__li_d38156e1_d38157e1_d38158e1\">\n<a class=\"xref\" data-bundleid=\"uniface_104\" data-navpath=\"fel1665702689477.html\" href=\"/de-DE/bundle/uniface_104/page/fel1665702689477.html\" title=\"Number of header lines displayed at the top of the component in character mode. The remainder of the form is scrolled. No default.\">Header Length</a>\n</li>\n<li class=\"li\" id=\"euw1665702582150__li_d38159e1_d38160e1_d38161e1\">\n<a class=\"xref\" data-bundleid=\"uniface_104\" data-navpath=\"lma1665702689548.html\" href=\"/de-DE/bundle/uniface_104/page/lma1665702689548.html\" title=\"Determines whether the screen is cleared before and after running a form that runs another form. Applicable only when the form is run in character mode. True or False (Default).\">Clear?</a>\n</li>\n<li class=\"li\" id=\"euw1665702582150__li_d38162e1_d38163e1_d38164e1\">\n<a class=\"xref\" data-bundleid=\"uniface_104\" data-navpath=\"rmo1665702689618.html\" href=\"/de-DE/bundle/uniface_104/page/rmo1665702689618.html\" title=\"Determines whether a rectangular border is displayed around the form component's outer edge in character mode.\">Borderline</a>\n</li>\n<li class=\"li\" id=\"euw1665702582150__li_d38165e1_d38166e1_d38167e1\">\n<a class=\"xref\" data-bundleid=\"uniface_104\" data-navpath=\"ngp1665702689690.html\" href=\"/de-DE/bundle/uniface_104/page/ngp1665702689690.html\" title=\"Display the field in reversed highlighting. Applicable only to Unifields.\">Inverse</a>\n</li>\n<li class=\"li\" id=\"euw1665702582150__li_d38168e1_d38169e1_d38170e1\">\n<a class=\"xref\" data-bundleid=\"uniface_104\" data-navpath=\"abx1665702689822.html\" href=\"/de-DE/bundle/uniface_104/page/abx1665702689822.html\" title=\"Display the field as bold. Applicable only to Unifields.\">Bright</a>\n</li>\n<li class=\"li\" id=\"euw1665702582150__li_d38171e1_d38172e1_d38173e1\">\n<a class=\"xref\" data-bundleid=\"uniface_104\" data-navpath=\"lhp1665702689890.html\" href=\"/de-DE/bundle/uniface_104/page/lhp1665702689890.html\" title=\"Display the field as underlined. Applicable only to Unifields.\">Underline</a>\n</li>\n<li class=\"li\" id=\"euw1665702582150__li_d38174e1_d38175e1_d38176e1\">\n<a class=\"xref\" data-bundleid=\"uniface_104\" data-navpath=\"avq1665702689959.html\" href=\"/de-DE/bundle/uniface_104/page/avq1665702689959.html\" title=\"Apply blinking to the field. Applicable only to Unifields.\">Blink</a>\n</li>\n</ul>\n</section>\n<section class=\"section\" id=\"euw1665702582150__section_om2_nrn_mwb\"><h2 class=\"title sectiontitle\" id=\"d497811e773\">Triggers and Operations</h2>\n<ul class=\"ul\" id=\"euw1665702582150__ul_kct_d5n_mwb\">\n<li class=\"li\" id=\"euw1665702582150__li_d38177e1_d38178e1_d38179e1\">\n<a class=\"xref\" data-bundleid=\"uniface_104\" data-navpath=\"kez1665702582531.html\" href=\"/de-DE/bundle/uniface_104/page/kez1665702582531.html\" title=\"Handles processing when an Accept request is received, usually with the intention of closing the component and keeping all changes made on it. This trigger is exposed as an operation in the component signature.\">trigger accept</a>\n</li>\n<li class=\"li\" id=\"euw1665702582150__li_d38180e1_d38181e1_d38182e1\">\n<a class=\"xref\" data-bundleid=\"uniface_104\" data-navpath=\"aag1665703130023.html\" href=\"/de-DE/bundle/uniface_104/page/aag1665703130023.html\" title=\"Trigger that reacts to the user's request to start over with a clean form.\">trigger clear</a>\n</li>\n<li class=\"li\" id=\"euw1665702582150__li_d38183e1_d38184e1_d38185e1\">\n<a class=\"xref\" data-bundleid=\"uniface_104\" data-navpath=\"two1665703130263.html\" href=\"/de-DE/bundle/uniface_104/page/two1665703130263.html\" title=\"Trigger that deletes all occurrences currently in the component, both in the external structure, and in the database. This is a very dangerous trigger—use it with extreme care!\">trigger erase</a>\n</li>\n<li class=\"li\" id=\"euw1665702582150__li_d38186e1_d38187e1_d38188e1\">\n<a class=\"xref\" data-bundleid=\"uniface_104\" data-navpath=\"jzq1665702665465.html\" href=\"/de-DE/bundle/uniface_104/page/jzq1665702665465.html\" title=\"Interactive trigger that responds to the form getting focus.\">trigger getFocus (Form)</a>\n</li>\n<li class=\"li\" id=\"euw1665702582150__li_d38189e1_d38190e1_d38191e1\">\n<a class=\"xref\" data-bundleid=\"uniface_104\" data-navpath=\"oxi1665702665543.html\" href=\"/de-DE/bundle/uniface_104/page/oxi1665702665543.html\" title=\"ProcScript module that responds to the form losing focus. It can be used to verify the data to ensure that it is complete or correct.\">trigger loseFocus (Form)</a>\n</li>\n<li class=\"li\" id=\"euw1665702582150__li_d38192e1_d38193e1_d38194e1\">\n<a class=\"xref\" data-bundleid=\"uniface_104\" data-navpath=\"xye1665702608643.html\" href=\"/de-DE/bundle/uniface_104/page/xye1665702608643.html\" title=\"Trigger that responds to a request for a menu in a desktop application.\">trigger menu</a>\n</li>\n<li class=\"li\" id=\"euw1665702582150__li_d38195e1_d38196e1_d38197e1\">\n<a class=\"xref\" data-bundleid=\"uniface_104\" data-navpath=\"hmh1665703130535.html\" href=\"/de-DE/bundle/uniface_104/page/hmh1665703130535.html\" title=\"Location for ProcScript that retrieves data from the database.\">trigger retrieve</a></li>\n<li class=\"li\" id=\"euw1665702582150__li_d38198e1_d38199e1_d38200e1\">\n<a class=\"xref\" data-bundleid=\"uniface_104\" data-navpath=\"jno1665702661208.html\" href=\"/de-DE/bundle/uniface_104/page/jno1665702661208.html\" title=\"Trigger that retrieves the next occurrence in the database with a primary key value greater than the current one.\">trigger retrieveSequential</a>\n</li>\n<li class=\"li\" id=\"euw1665702582150__li_d38201e1_d38202e1_d38203e1\">\n<a class=\"xref\" data-bundleid=\"uniface_104\" data-navpath=\"hmn1665702683413.html\" href=\"/de-DE/bundle/uniface_104/page/hmn1665702683413.html\" title=\"System trigger that provides component-specific post-processing.\">trigger postActivate</a>\n</li>\n<li class=\"li\" id=\"euw1665702582150__li_d38204e1_d38205e1_d38206e1\">\n<a class=\"xref\" data-bundleid=\"uniface_104\" data-navpath=\"muo1665702683268.html\" href=\"/de-DE/bundle/uniface_104/page/muo1665702683268.html\" title=\"System trigger that provides component-specific pre-processing. It is required in web applications to recreate the component state.\">trigger preActivate</a>\n</li>\n<li class=\"li\" id=\"euw1665702582150__li_d38207e1_d38208e1_d38209e1\">\n<a class=\"xref\" data-bundleid=\"uniface_104\" data-navpath=\"ita1665703130455.html\" href=\"/de-DE/bundle/uniface_104/page/ita1665703130455.html\" title=\"Interactive trigger for responding to a print request.\">trigger print</a>\n</li>\n<li class=\"li\" id=\"euw1665702582150__li_d38210e1_d38211e1_d38212e1\">\n<a class=\"xref\" data-bundleid=\"uniface_104\" data-navpath=\"sux1665703129629.html\" href=\"/de-DE/bundle/uniface_104/page/sux1665703129629.html\" title=\"Interactive trigger for responding to a request for a pulldown menu in a desktop application.\">trigger pullDown</a></li>\n<li class=\"li\" id=\"euw1665702582150__li_d38213e1_d38214e1_d38215e1\">\n<a class=\"xref\" data-bundleid=\"uniface_104\" data-navpath=\"ghq1665702608876.html\" href=\"/de-DE/bundle/uniface_104/page/ghq1665702608876.html\" title=\"Reacts to asynchronous messages that come from outside the application.\">trigger receiveMessage</a>\n</li>\n<li class=\"li\" id=\"euw1665702582150__li_d38216e1_d38217e1_d38218e1\">\n<a class=\"xref\" data-bundleid=\"uniface_104\" data-navpath=\"jvb1665703130778.html\" href=\"/de-DE/bundle/uniface_104/page/jvb1665703130778.html\" title=\"Trigger that responds to a request to save (store) the data.\">trigger store</a></li>\n<li class=\"li\" id=\"euw1665702582150__li_d38219e1_d38220e1_d38221e1\">\n<a class=\"xref\" data-bundleid=\"uniface_104\" data-navpath=\"qun1665702582075.html\" href=\"/de-DE/bundle/uniface_104/page/qun1665702582075.html\" title=\"Trigger that handles processing when a Quit request is received, usually with the intention of closing the component without saving any modifications made in it. This trigger is exposed as an operation in the component signature.\">trigger quit</a>\n</li>\n<li class=\"li\" id=\"euw1665702582150__li_d38222e1_d38223e1_d38224e1\">\n<a class=\"xref\" data-bundleid=\"uniface_104\" data-navpath=\"niy1665702606431.html\" href=\"/de-DE/bundle/uniface_104/page/niy1665702606431.html\" title=\"Trigger for responding to user-defined key sequences as defined in the Keyboard Translation Table (KTT) or defined in the usys.ini section named as userkeys.\">trigger userKey</a>\n</li>\n</ul>\n<ul class=\"ul\" id=\"euw1665702582150__ul_pdt_d5n_mwb\">\n<li class=\"li\" id=\"euw1665702582150__li_d38225e1_d38226e1_d38227e1\">\n<a class=\"xref\" data-bundleid=\"uniface_104\" data-navpath=\"mkf1719505969039.html\" href=\"/de-DE/bundle/uniface_104/page/mkf1719505969039.html\" title=\"Default component operation, which is invoked by the activate statement.\">operation exec</a>\n</li>\n<li class=\"li\" id=\"euw1665702582150__li_d38228e1_d38229e1_d38230e1\">\n<a class=\"xref\" data-bundleid=\"uniface_104\" data-navpath=\"zye1719506814289.html\" href=\"/de-DE/bundle/uniface_104/page/zye1719506814289.html\" title=\"Defines the component behavior when a component instance is created with newinstance (or by activate when newinstance is executed implicitly).\">operation init</a>\n</li>\n<li class=\"li\" id=\"euw1665702582150__li_d38231e1_d38232e1_d38233e1\">\n<a class=\"xref\" data-bundleid=\"uniface_104\" data-navpath=\"tcd1719504517290.html\" href=\"/de-DE/bundle/uniface_104/page/tcd1719504517290.html\" title=\"Defines the component behavior when a component instance is removed.\">operation cleanup</a>\n</li>\n<li class=\"li\" id=\"euw1665702582150__li_d38234e1_d38235e1_d38236e1\">\n<a class=\"xref\" data-bundleid=\"uniface_104\" data-navpath=\"tdr1719503726176.html\" href=\"/de-DE/bundle/uniface_104/page/tdr1719503726176.html\" title=\"Defines the behavior that should occur in response to an Accept request. If an Accept trigger is defined, it is exposed as the accept operation in the component signature.\">operation accept</a></li>\n<li class=\"li\" id=\"euw1665702582150__li_d38237e1_d38238e1_d38239e1\">\n<a class=\"xref\" data-bundleid=\"uniface_104\" data-navpath=\"icw1719507043571.html\" href=\"/de-DE/bundle/uniface_104/page/icw1719507043571.html\" title=\"Defines the processing that should occur during a Quit request. If a quit trigger is defined in a component, it is exposed as the quit operation in the component signature.\">operation quit</a>\n</li>\n</ul>\n</section>\n</div>\n</article></main></article>\n</div></div></div><div class=\"bottomFeedback\"><div aria-labelledby=\"bottomFeedbackText\" class=\"bottomFeedbackContent\" role=\"group\"><span class=\"bottomFeedbackText\" id=\"bottomFeedbackText\">Was this topic helpful?</span><div class=\"bottomFeedbackButtonGroup\"><a data-backdrop=\"static\" data-target=\"#feedbackModal_bottom_3612899\" data-toggle=\"modal\" href=\"#\" role=\"button\" type=\"button\"><svg aria-hidden=\"true\" class=\"ico-thumbs-up\"><use xlink:href=\"#ico-thumbs-up\"></use></svg><span>Like</span></a><a data-backdrop=\"static\" data-target=\"#feedbackModal_bottom_3612899\" data-toggle=\"modal\" href=\"#\" role=\"button\" type=\"button\"><svg aria-hidden=\"true\" class=\"ico-thumbs-down\"><use xlink:href=\"#ico-thumbs-down\"></use></svg><span>Dislike</span></a></div></div></div><div style=\"position: fixed; bottom: 170px; right: 70px; cursor: pointer; transition-duration: 0.2s; transition-timing-function: linear; transition-delay: 0s; z-index: 3; opacity: 0; visibility: hidden; transition-property: opacity, visibility;\"><button aria-label=\"Scroll to top\" class=\"zDocsScrollTopBtn\" data-tooltip-content=\"Scroll to top\" data-tooltip-id=\"zDocsBackToTopToolTip\" id=\"zDocsScrollToTop\" type=\"button\"><svg aria-hidden=\"true\" class=\"ico-next\"><use xlink:href=\"#ico-next\"></use></svg></button></div></body></html>", "text": "Form Add to My Topics Add selected topic and subtopics Add Topic & Subtopics with topic head Add entire publication Watch Download PDF Save selected topic Save selected topic and subtopics Save entire publication Share Email Link Copy Link Feedback Last Updated Okt 09, 2024 Summarize Uniface 10.4 Form A Form is a stateful presentation Component that enables users to view and modify data in a Windows or character mode application. Characteristics Characteristics Icon: Object type code: cpt Main Development Object? Yes Has layout? Yes Layout binding? Implicit Part of: — Contains: Component Entity , Label , Property , Code Container Generalization: Component Specializations: — Compilation Output: Signature , FormName .frm , FormName .sig URI format: cpt: FormName Specialization Form specializes Component in the following ways: It has a layout that is part of the component itself. It has specialized triggers. It compiles to a deployable runtime component ( .frm ) and signature. Properties Object Properties: Name Type Location Description Documentation Source Properties: Date Modified Configuration Properties: Library Is Modeled Component Modeled Component Behavior Properties: Component Type Data Access Component Behavior Attachment Database I/O Properties: Input Translation Output Translation Presentation Properties: Window Properties Title Panel Panel Position Menu Bar Pop-up Menu Is Independent Form Hide Previous Index Color Top Left Height Width Character Mode Properties: Header Length Clear? Borderline Inverse Bright Underline Blink Triggers and Operations trigger accept trigger clear trigger erase trigger getFocus (Form) trigger loseFocus (Form) trigger menu trigger retrieve trigger retrieveSequential trigger postActivate trigger preActivate trigger print trigger pullDown trigger receiveMessage trigger store trigger quit trigger userKey operation exec operation init operation cleanup operation accept operation quit Was this topic helpful? Like Dislike"}